snippet.title: E-sport: Ako vzniká esportový tím na Slovensku. E-sport team Amber. Dá sa uživiť e-sportom?
snippet.description:
Sledujeme začiatky vzniku nového esportového tímu Amber. Prečo vznikol, aké má ciele a aké sú šance na jeho úspech? Rozprávame sa s kapitánom tímu Peťom Kučerom, hráčom FIFA2020 Peťom Dubašákom a ambasádorkou tímu, známou hráčkou NHL2020, Sandrou Demitrovou. Sami zhodnoťte ambície tímu Amber, prípadne sa staňte ich prvými fanúšikmi. Preniknite spolu s nimi do zákulisia elektronického športu, prípadne ich navštívte na Majstrovstvách v elektronických športoch MSR, kde budú hrať CS:GO.

snippet.title: AMBER Alert: Dive team called to search area for missing 5-year-old Summer Wells
snippet.description:
The Tennessee Bureau of Investigation says all avenues are being explored in the search for missing 5-year-old Summer Wells, the child at the center of a Tennessee AMBER Alert.

By the end of Friday, 41 law enforcement agencies are expected to have combed through 1,000 acres of steep and dangerous terrain for Summer. Dive crews have now been called to the search area that includes multiple ponds and streams. More than 100 trained professionals on the ground, K9s, helicopters and hazards teams all share the same ultimate goal of finding Summer Wells.

“We are pursuing every avenue. We’re covering every ground area, every aspect,” a search captain said. “We want to flip every rock, check every crevice.”

Currently, the TBI has two main aspects of the investigation: the ongoing search itself for Summer and the investigation into how she disappeared.

More on this story:  https://fox17.com/news/local/tennessee-amber-alert-issued-for-missing-5-year-old-girl-hawkins-county-tbi-summer-moon-utah-wells-investigation
